column4: Maddox is Armenian the same way Keeping Up with the Kardashians is Armenian.
Maddox is a man like Lord Varys is a man.
I'm in Armenia for work and tell anyone who speaks English about how a cuck named Maddox is bringing shame to their land.

in a disputed territory in azerbaijan there was a fruity armenian italian guy named Alex. Alex had two concerns at the forefront of his mind anytime we went anywhere: what's the wifi password, and telling me who he would and would not fuck. For a few days we stayed with a host family who had two beautiful daughters and one not so beautiful daughter. in this area it's custom to get your guests retard drunk during and after dinner. Alex spent about an hour goinf on during dinner about how he wants to fuck the two daughters but cannot bring himself to try and fuck the other daughter. He would movw his hands wildly and and speak in a small voice about wanting to fuck just about everyone really, and every day he'd tell me how thankful he was that I was so strong.
Boisterous Coconuts once called the Kardashians the only Armenians nobody feels sorry for. You can add Saddox to that list.
